description: FastPartner AB engages in the acquisition, development, and management of real estate. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 82 full-time employees.  The firm focuses on managing commercial properties principally in Stockholm, as well as in Gavle, Sweden, among others. The company offers premises primarily adjusted for offices, warehouses, shops and production areas. The firm also offers combined facilities, which are adapted to a variety of activities. The Company’s portfolio also includes residential properties and hotels. The firm operates through a number of wholly owned subsidiaries. In July 2014, the Company acquired property Skebo 2 located in Lunda, Stockholm, which comprises warehouses and offices.
name: FastPartner AB
